1
00:01:52,300 --> 00:01:53,730
Reporting...

2
00:01:54,010 --> 00:01:58,470
The rebelling human vermin have connected 
the Dragon Chain Cannon to the giant lacrima

3
00:01:58,470 --> 00:02:01,100
and are trying to crash it into Extalia.

4
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:06,560
Nichiya-sama, as well as the majority of the 
Royal Guard, have been turned into a lacrima,

5
00:02:06,980 --> 00:02:08,980
and are now being held 
captive in the Royal City.

6
00:02:09,740 --> 00:02:11,630
At this rate, Extalia...

7
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:14,800
How incredibly reckless!

8
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,620
Fearsome indeed!

9
00:02:16,620 --> 00:02:19,630
To think they would go so far...

10
00:02:20,100 --> 00:02:23,440
Furthermore, one of the Fallen and 
a human have appeared in the town,

11
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:26,200
and are spreading the word to 
abandon Extalia and escape...

12
00:02:26,570 --> 00:02:30,620
They're causing a riot outside of the 
castle... How should we deal with the situation?

13
00:02:33,070 --> 00:02:35,210
Lead me there.

14
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,880
What?!

15
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:38,050
My Queen!

16
00:02:38,050 --> 00:02:39,910
What are you intending to do?

17
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:41,090
The time...

18
00:02:42,490 --> 00:02:44,190
The time has come.

19
00:02:47,990 --> 00:02:49,970
The Boy Back Then.

20
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:57,440
Gajeel!

21
00:02:58,130 --> 00:03:01,530
Hurry and destroy the lacrima and 
turn everyone back to normal!

22
00:03:02,010 --> 00:03:03,410
I won't make it...

23
00:03:04,070 --> 00:03:05,630
It's accelerating, damn it!

24
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:06,800
Oh, no!

25
00:03:08,830 --> 00:03:12,150
Hurry!

26
00:03:12,150 --> 00:03:16,330
We can't let it collide!

27
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:25,990
Hang in there, Legy-pyon!

28
00:03:31,230 --> 00:03:33,790
It's no use! We're not coming 
even close to stopping it!

29
00:03:33,790 --> 00:03:36,270
Everyone, release your magic power!

30
00:03:36,270 --> 00:03:39,030
Please, stop!

31
00:03:43,450 --> 00:03:45,640
Stop!

32
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:51,660
Natsu!

33
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,880
I...

34
00:03:56,750 --> 00:03:57,990
Um...

35
00:04:02,070 --> 00:04:04,340
Help me out, partner!

36
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:10,230
Aye, sir!

37
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:14,790
We'll finish this later, cat!

38
00:04:14,790 --> 00:04:15,900
Running for it?

39
00:04:15,900 --> 00:04:17,810
I ain't runnin' or hidin'!

40
00:04:17,810 --> 00:04:20,490
I'm gonna stop this thing and finish this!

41
00:04:20,490 --> 00:04:22,830
Stop it? You're going to <i>stop</i> it?

42
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:25,700
The entire floating island 
connected to the Dragon Chain?

43
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,480
That's a fool's errand!

44
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,560
There is no tomorrow for us.

45
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:32,040
We have nothing left!

46
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,330
Hey!

47
00:04:33,660 --> 00:04:34,970
<i>After</i> this...

48
00:04:34,970 --> 00:04:37,400
...I'm taking you back to my 
guild one way or the other!

49
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:40,260
And then I'm gonna make you my cat.

50
00:04:50,220 --> 00:04:52,040
It's no use, they're going to hit!

51
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:53,680
Brace for it!

52
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:59,690
Damn it all!!

53
00:05:09,660 --> 00:05:11,620
Not yet!

54
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:13,420
Don't give up, Happy!

55
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:14,660
Aye, sir!

56
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:18,670
Gajeel?

57
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:22,870
Why haven't you returned everyone 
else to normal like us?

58
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:24,290
You have to hurry!

59
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:26,680
That black cat got in my way!

60
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:30,100
It doesn't matter. It'd 
take too much time now!

61
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:31,380
We have no choice but to stop it!

62
00:05:31,610 --> 00:05:34,060
We're totally gonna stop it, damn it!

63
00:05:34,650 --> 00:05:37,120
Coco, why are you...

64
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,270
Lily!

65
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:43,350
I realized that I don't 
need eternal magic power!

66
00:05:43,670 --> 00:05:45,740
I'd rather have eternal smiles!

67
00:05:45,740 --> 00:05:47,810
What foolishness!

68
00:05:47,810 --> 00:05:49,650
Hurry up and escape, Coco!

69
00:05:49,650 --> 00:05:52,900
No matter what you do, you'll 
never stop this island!

70
00:05:52,900 --> 00:05:54,410
We'll stop it...

71
00:05:54,410 --> 00:05:59,350
Even if this body crumbles to bits, 
I'll stop it just with my soul!!

72
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:02,930
Aye, sir!

73
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:14,870
Dear...

74
00:06:15,900 --> 00:06:18,390
What the hell is goin' on?

75
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,730
The Royal Army is attacking!

76
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:25,730
The humans are attacking!

77
00:06:25,730 --> 00:06:27,980
They're planning on rebelling 
against the Exceed?

78
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:29,910
Those damn humans don't 
realize our Queen's power...

79
00:06:28,660 --> 00:06:30,620
You'll learn some respect today!

80
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:33,470
I'm sure our Queen's magic 
will come out anytime now!

81
00:06:33,470 --> 00:06:37,210
Sure, but I hope we counterattack soon, or...

82
00:06:36,170 --> 00:06:39,460
Don't be afraid! Our Queen is with us!

83
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:41,370
The lacrima hit...

84
00:06:41,370 --> 00:06:44,540
It's not done yet. It seems to have 
stopped at the edge of the island.

85
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:46,220
I'm sorry, Carla...

86
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,380
It wasn't supposed to turn out like...

87
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:51,980
What are you saying? It's 
too early to give up hope!

88
00:06:53,910 --> 00:06:55,390
Everyone, listen!

89
00:06:56,070 --> 00:06:58,570
You're still here, you Fallen?!

90
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,390
Nady-sama?

91
00:07:03,700 --> 00:07:04,610
Carla!

92
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:11,030
T-Throwing stones... is... dangerous...

93
00:07:12,550 --> 00:07:14,170
But she's a Fallen...

94
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:18,460
These people came here to warn us of danger!

95
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:21,540
But because no one listened to 
them, it's turned out like this!

96
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:23,330
What are you saying?

97
00:07:23,330 --> 00:07:26,800
With our Queen's magic, something 
like this is no problem!

98
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:28,770
Now, the Queen will...

99
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:37,260
Uh... Um...

100
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:39,750
Enough, Nady.

101
00:07:42,470 --> 00:07:44,000
My Queen!

102
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:46,520
It's the Queen!

103
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:54,610
My Queen!

104
00:07:55,470 --> 00:07:57,550
That person is the Queen?

105
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:10,640
Everyone, please raise your heads.

106
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:14,680
Then listen calmly to what I am about to say.

107
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:17,600
Why is the Queen here?

108
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,720
'Cause I bet she's gonna do some 
incredibly destructive magic...

109
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,720
Shh! Quiet!

110
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:25,700
Right now, Extalia is on the 
brink of complete destruction.

111
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:28,280
It is a fate we can no longer resist.

112
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:32,420
Therefore, I have made a decision.

113
00:08:32,420 --> 00:08:34,700
You're gonna wipe out all the humans, right?

114
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:35,950
Stay silent and listen!

115
00:08:38,990 --> 00:08:40,870
W-What is it, Queen?

116
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:49,590
I decided that I must 
tell everyone the truth.

117
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,230
I am simply an Exceed.

118
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:56,700
I am hardly a Queen, and 
most definitely not a god.

119
00:08:57,100 --> 00:09:00,530
I am an Exceed, the same as you all.

120
00:09:00,530 --> 00:09:02,410
N-No!

121
00:09:02,410 --> 00:09:06,610
I have no power to fight the humans.

122
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:11,270
As you can see, I am one-winged.

123
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:16,520
For an Exceed, one's wings grow and 
shrink by one's own magic power.

124
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:19,780
With both wings, one can display 
one's true magic power.

125
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:23,790
My magic power is extremely weak.

126
00:09:24,750 --> 00:09:27,830
I am so sorry I hid all of this...

127
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:31,120
You are Wendy-san and Carla-san, yes?

128
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,560
I must apologize to you as well.

129
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,970
This is all my fault.

130
00:09:35,970 --> 00:09:39,470
Please, do not hate me, everyone.

131
00:09:39,770 --> 00:09:41,800
What is going on?

132
00:09:43,260 --> 00:09:49,240
The ones who created the 
"Queen" were we elders.

133
00:09:49,810 --> 00:09:53,560
We are a very weak race.

134
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:58,280
Since long ago, we have had terrible 
things done to us by the humans.

135
00:09:58,860 --> 00:10:06,780
Therefore, to protect ourselves, we made 
the humans believe that we had power.

136
00:10:06,780 --> 00:10:11,000
Then, for all Exceeds to gain 
back their self-confidence,

137
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:16,050
we had everyone in Extalia believe that 
they were protected by the power of God.

138
00:10:17,170 --> 00:10:24,340
The power of God was nothing more than 
a bluff known only to us few Exceeds...

139
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:27,540
At first, the humans didn't believe us,

140
00:10:27,540 --> 00:10:32,010
but before long they began 
to fear the power of God...

141
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:37,830
For example, the Human Control 
that decides when humans die...

142
00:10:37,830 --> 00:10:40,170
It's all actually after the fact.

143
00:10:40,170 --> 00:10:43,720
We don't decide what humans are killed...

144
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:46,130
We don't have such power, of course.

145
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:51,730
The only thing we have is that Chagot 
can see a little bit into the future.

146
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:54,640
She can see people's deaths.

147
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:59,840
When she was correct, we made people 
think it was she who killed them.

148
00:11:00,890 --> 00:11:03,020
It's a lie!

149
00:11:04,850 --> 00:11:07,580
Our Queen is God!

150
00:11:07,580 --> 00:11:11,660
Chagot-sama, hurry and destroy the humans!

151
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:14,410
We were deceived!

152
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:16,630
Carla?

153
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:21,730
Whether or not you actually have power, 
you ordered me to kill my friends!

154
00:11:21,730 --> 00:11:23,160
That I know to be the truth!

155
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:26,000
Chagot never gave such an order!

156
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:28,600
It must have been the humans 
who used the Queen to...

157
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,120
No!

158
00:11:29,620 --> 00:11:33,170
You placed strange memories, 
messing with my head!

159
00:11:33,170 --> 00:11:35,940
You ordered me to eliminate 
the Dragon Slayers, yes?

160
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:37,750
Since before I even hatched!

161
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:39,880
That's...

162
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:44,180
N-N-N-N-No! There's a really long, 
important reason for that...

163
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:46,850
Even if there is a reason, 
I'll never forgive you!

164
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:50,040
Carla, now is really not the time...

165
00:11:59,050 --> 00:12:01,570
Carla-san is completely correct.

166
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:04,190
You had no sin in this.

167
00:12:04,690 --> 00:12:07,700
And yet, I made you bear the 
most painful feelings of all.

168
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:10,440
Q-Queen!

169
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:13,910
Please pass judgment on me 
for my sins by your own hand!

170
00:12:25,710 --> 00:12:27,680
Pass judgment by your own hands!

171
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:34,700
You, who love both the Exceed and 
the Humans, have such a right!

172
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:35,980
Carla...

173
00:12:37,130 --> 00:12:38,980
Queen!

174
00:12:38,980 --> 00:12:40,370
Queen!

175
00:12:43,850 --> 00:12:46,620
Now everyone, get away from here!

176
00:12:46,620 --> 00:12:50,030
My fate lies alongside 
Extalia as it falls to ruin!

177
00:12:52,170 --> 00:12:53,800
Carla...

178
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:54,750
Stop this!

179
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:58,740
We don't want to leave you...

180
00:12:58,740 --> 00:13:01,040
I'll stay here!

181
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:03,550
This is the end of our history...

182
00:13:03,550 --> 00:13:06,230
That's why the Queen felt she 
had to tell us everything...

183
00:13:08,410 --> 00:13:11,110
But I want to be with you, Queen!

184
00:13:11,110 --> 00:13:13,630
I want to stay here, too!

185
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:17,140
Everyone, you can't! This country 
is fated for destruction!

186
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:20,820
Carla!!

187
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:32,870
How dare...

188
00:13:33,470 --> 00:13:35,880
How dare you just give up?!

189
00:13:37,650 --> 00:13:39,550
This is your country, right?

190
00:13:40,090 --> 00:13:43,240
Can't you do anything 
without a god or queen?!

191
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:47,400
Didn't you try your best to 
live on, even if it was a lie?

192
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,700
So why are you giving up so easily?

193
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:52,480
So what if you're weak?

194
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:55,920
If everyone works together, 
you can accomplish anything!

195
00:13:57,900 --> 00:14:00,130
This country will not be destroyed!

196
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:02,550
Because it's my homeland!

197
00:14:03,050 --> 00:14:05,530
It isn't going anywhere!

198
00:14:10,470 --> 00:14:12,200
I won't give up.

199
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,920
I'll stop it, no matter what!

200
00:14:14,740 --> 00:14:15,850
Carla!

201
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:28,950
I'll go, too.

202
00:14:28,950 --> 00:14:29,880
Nady...

203
00:14:32,590 --> 00:14:35,980
After all, I love this country!

204
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:43,440
I think I'm gonna be crushed!

205
00:14:46,690 --> 00:14:48,580
Hold on!

206
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:50,530
We have to stop this... We have to!

207
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,950
It's pointless...

208
00:14:56,950 --> 00:15:01,150
This isn't something humans can do anything 
about, no matter how strong they are!

209
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,590
Carla?

210
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:11,750
I'm not going to give up... on 
Fairy Tail... or on Extalia!

211
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:14,510
I'm gonna protect them both!

212
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,670
You're...

213
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:26,700
I wanna protect it, too!

214
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:29,490
And I bet everyone else does, too...

215
00:15:34,990 --> 00:15:37,870
This is... What's going on?

216
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,080
That light...

217
00:15:58,260 --> 00:16:01,620
We'll protect our country ourselves!

218
00:16:01,620 --> 00:16:05,000
We came through dangerous times and 
protected our country and its people!

219
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,620
For our Queen!

220
00:16:06,620 --> 00:16:10,320
Wendy-san, Carla-san... 
We're sorry about before!

221
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:13,490
Everyone, we've got to do 
something about this now!

222
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:17,900
Chagot, with your wing, you can't...

223
00:16:17,900 --> 00:16:21,120
No, I must!

224
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:23,250
I must do what I can!

225
00:16:24,540 --> 00:16:26,610
What dream is this?

226
00:16:27,250 --> 00:16:29,630
Extalia has joined together as one...

227
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:47,030
Lily, why did you save a human?

228
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:48,900
Because the child was seriously wounded...

229
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:54,200
Fool! Bringing that <i>thing</i> to 
Extalia is a grave offense!

230
00:16:54,200 --> 00:16:58,600
However, I must help the 
injured, even if they be human.

231
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:01,320
You didn't forget the rules, right, Lily?

232
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:05,280
You are now made one of the Fallen, 
and are banished from Extalia!

233
00:17:05,590 --> 00:17:08,140
What?! For this?!

234
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:23,600
What?

235
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:28,530
Don't worry... It wasn't 
your fault I was banished.

236
00:17:29,010 --> 00:17:31,830
First thing I must do is escort you home.

237
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:35,680
Queen!

238
00:17:43,740 --> 00:17:44,700
Lily!

239
00:17:52,030 --> 00:17:53,420
My Queen...

240
00:17:54,470 --> 00:17:57,770
Are you tired from lying?

241
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:02,960
I'm sorry... I...

242
00:18:04,150 --> 00:18:05,270
As am I...

243
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:11,810
No matter how much I may resent 
it, Extalia is my country!

244
00:18:12,650 --> 00:18:13,730
Lily...

245
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,780
But, it's too late.

246
00:18:17,130 --> 00:18:21,100
Even with this many Exceed, 
they can't stop it.

247
00:18:21,660 --> 00:18:25,160
I'm sorry, everyone! This is my fault!

248
00:18:25,670 --> 00:18:27,580
I could have stopped them!

249
00:18:27,580 --> 00:18:31,880
I could have stopped the humans!

250
00:18:34,470 --> 00:18:39,090
Your feelings... I know your 
feelings will get through!

251
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:42,030
Stop!!

252
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,550
Everyone, go for it!

253
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:45,900
Push!

254
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:48,190
We can do it!

255
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:51,150
We ain't gonna lose!

256
00:18:51,150 --> 00:18:53,860
We shall ne'er give up!

257
00:18:56,730 --> 00:18:59,300
We're gonna stop it, for sure!

258
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:00,750
We'll push, too!

259
00:19:00,750 --> 00:19:02,470
Aye, sir!

260
00:19:07,060 --> 00:19:08,790
Aye, sir!

261
00:19:09,050 --> 00:19:13,260
Aye, aye, sir!

262
00:19:13,260 --> 00:19:16,000
Please, stop!!

263
00:19:24,790 --> 00:19:27,370
The lacrima is being pushed back..

264
00:19:31,690 --> 00:19:32,610
What?

265
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:14,080
Carla?

266
00:20:14,490 --> 00:20:15,660
Look at that.

267
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:23,860
That's...

268
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:41,560
The lacrima has disappeared...

269
00:20:42,140 --> 00:20:44,250
The Dragon Chain Cannon's chain as well...

270
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:45,680
W-What's going on?

271
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:49,070
It has been returned to Earthland.

272
00:20:52,620 --> 00:20:53,920
Mystogan!

273
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:58,000
I searched for the remaining tear from the 
giant Anima to return everything to the way it was.

274
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,560
I apologize for my lateness.

275
00:21:00,690 --> 00:21:03,480
Without everyone's help, 
I wouldn't have made it.

276
00:21:03,780 --> 00:21:04,730
I give you my thanks.

277
00:21:05,290 --> 00:21:07,280
The way it was?

278
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:08,490
That's right.

279
00:21:09,020 --> 00:21:13,480
The lacrima has passed once again through the 
Anima and returned to how it was in Earthland.

280
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:16,370
Everything is over.

281
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:19,270
We did it?

282
00:21:19,270 --> 00:21:22,950
We protected Extalia!

283
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:37,480
Lily, you saved my life.

284
00:21:38,230 --> 00:21:40,560
I am glad I was able to 
protect your homeland...

285
00:21:48,300 --> 00:21:50,030
Thank you very much...

286
00:21:50,760 --> 00:21:51,850
...Prince.

287
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:54,730
The Prince is back!

288
00:21:54,730 --> 00:21:55,790
Prince?

289
00:22:07,130 --> 00:22:08,600
Black cat!

290
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,810
Lily!

291
00:22:16,650 --> 00:22:17,430
This isn't over!

292
00:22:18,900 --> 00:22:20,900
This isn't over yet!

293
00:23:55,800 --> 00:23:58,960
Hey, Happy, there's a dragon-looking 
thing out there...

294
00:23:58,960 --> 00:24:01,600
Wasn't there something like that before?

295
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:05,810
I think you're talking about the 
Dragonoid... But this one looks different.

296
00:24:05,810 --> 00:24:07,990
They're both just fake dragons, right?

297
00:24:07,990 --> 00:24:09,550
I'll bust it up like I did the last one!

298
00:24:09,550 --> 00:24:13,840
Be careful. If it's just coming out 
now, there must be something to it.

299
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:16,470
Next time: Dragon Sense!

300
00:24:16,470 --> 00:24:19,170
What's with this thing? 
Magic doesn't work on it?

301
00:24:19,170 --> 00:24:21,510
Look, Natsu! It's changing color!

302
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:24,560
I guess this isn't dragon 
slaying, it's chameleon slaying.

